description:
This promotion is available to all registered users who are eligible to receive promotions.

Every day at 00:01 UTC, twenty-five qualifying players will be randomly selected in a daily raffle.

The daily prize is 500 EUR, but if it is not claimed by 23:59 UTC on the same day, it will be added to the grand jackpot bank. The grand jackpot can reach up to 5,000 EUR.

To claim the prize, the winning player needs to log in before 23:59 UTC on the same day and click the "Claim" button in the Congratulations pop-up.

Once claimed, the prize will be added to the user's account balance within 12 hours.

The prize is subject to 0× wagering requirements, which must be completed within 10 days of claiming the prize.

This promotion is not limited in time. However, our Website reserves the right to modify or terminate the promotion at its discretion and without prior notice.

This promotion is valid in accordance with the Terms and Conditions.
